description.displayText: We found Ellen through care to look after our children and our friends' children who were visiting us from overseas. She was wonderful, she took over as soon as she entered the apartment. The children all seemed to connect with her. She was punctual and even cleared up the dinner dishes! Would highly recommend her.

description.displayText: I found Ellen through care.com last year and she has worked for us part time for a year.  Our children are going to be in school from this fall but I can't speak too highly of Ellen as a child caregiver.  She is super responsible, punctual, very honest.  She is engaging and creative with kids.  We are still going to ask her to babysit our weekly date nights.
